title: Extracting Differences from an ArcSDE Geodatabase

questions.question: Versioning is supported for:
options: only the Enterprise Geodatabase (ArcSDE) and File Geodatabase.

questions.question: When you extract differences from geodatabase transactional versions or archives, FME automatically sets the fme_db_operation attribute to INSERT, UPDATE or DELETE.
It's acceptable to extract differences between different branches in your versioned geodatabase.
